        "r": "1PE.3.1",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.7": {
    "text": "For we have great joy and consolation in your love, because the hearts of the saints have been refreshed by you, brother.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.7.13",
        "v": 10
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.3.9",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.7.4",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.20",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "3JN.1.3-6",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.19",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "2JN.1.4",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2TI.1.16",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.1.3",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.13",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.8": {
    "text": "Therefore, though I might be very bold in Christ to command you what is fitting,",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.6",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.10.8",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.3.12",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.5.4",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.10.1-2",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.2",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.11.21",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": "The Plea for Onesimus"
  },
  "PHM.1.9": {
    "text": "yet for love’s sake I rather appeal to you—being such a one as Paul, the aged, and now also a prisoner of Jesus Christ—",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.12.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.5.20",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.1",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.1-25",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.2.11",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "ISA.46.4",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PSA.71.9",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PRO.16.31",
        "v": 1
