      {
        "r": "LUK.15.32",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.2.10",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.17.10",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.3.12",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.25.30",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.15.24",
        "v": 3
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.12": {
    "text": "I am sending him back. You therefore receive him, that is, my own heart,",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "MAT.6.14-15",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.18.21-35",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "JER.31.20",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.32",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "MRK.11.25",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.15.20",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "2SA.16.11",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "DEU.13.6",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.13": {
    "text": "whom I wished to keep with me, that on your behalf he might minister to me in my chains for the gospel.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "PHP.1.7",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.16.17",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.2.30",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.1",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.1",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.14": {
    "text": "But without your consent I wanted to do nothing, that your good deed might not be by compulsion, as it were, but voluntary.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.9.7",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.5.2-3",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CH.29.17",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.8-9",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.9.17",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.8.12",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.9.5",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.1.24",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PSA.110.3",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.15": {
    "text": "For perhaps he departed for a while for this purpose, that you might receive him forever,",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "GEN.50.20",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "GEN.45.5-8",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "ISA.20.6",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "ACT.4.28",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
